nodes.text: Aqualish beer was a type of beer in the galaxy. When Doctor Cornelius Evazan posed as Princess Leia Organa looking to hire Nokk and Winloss to destroy the Triple-Zero protocol personality matrix, and Ponda Baba had been disguised as a rebel trooper, Nokk rejected the job, adding that Organa's guard reeked of Aqualish beer and that there was something shady going on.
